room_title: Escape room "The Museum of Curiosity" by Exit Puzzles Escape Room in Tacoma
room_description: Olympia's greatest tourist trap 'The Museum of Curiosity' is threatened with closure, unless you and your team can help to unravel the museums curious past. See if you have what it takes to discover the mystery of the missing curator, and perhaps put an end to the alleged curse that has been brought to the museum.
